BFI Finance rose 1.1 percent to 4,700 rupiah.  PT Surya Semesta Internusa (SSIA)  : The industrial and
residential estate company may spend 750 billion rupiah to buy
1,500 hectares of land this year,  Bisnis Indonesia  reported,
citing President Director Johannes Suriadjaja. The stock fell
